{"tid":1701324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"是日五毛風向：法庭就係法治，法庭無法無天就係司法獨立","createTime":"2019-11-09T03:58:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T14:46:46.000Z","uid":51546,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e49c537dbf5e5d04c2229d6ef65b6546896d1102","tid":1701324,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:58:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真文宣核彈</span></span><br />\n<br />\n法治指以民意授權為前提和基礎立法，以嚴格依法管治國家為核心，以制約權力為關鍵的社會管理機制、社會活動方式和社會秩序狀態。法治的內涵，不單是要求所有人民守法，更側重於法律對政府權力的控制和拘束。 法治意味著每個人都受到法律的約束，包括立法者、行政官員和法官。"},{"pid":"fe22564fd021224b8072723d73b271f081d6ef64","tid":1701324,"uid":51546,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:58:52.000Z","msg":"破壞法治係特首法官"},{"pid":"b1de06940d4b10d011a522c7cd398f24c7f1b240","tid":1701324,"uid":51546,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:00:30.000Z","msg":"香港司法完全反法治<br />\n香港司法係政府防線"},{"pid":"115cd5df5d22e86c329aa4a99737f8f0b3c768f3","tid":1701324,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:02:02.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"9f7b06b7957dbe5a303a3324688e0fe0f6d1b8a7","tid":1701324,"uid":7484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:02:30.000Z","msg":"司法已死"},{"pid":"905245f582d517904bc3974420e8c45dcf13aaf7","tid":1701324,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"115cd5df5d22e86c329aa4a99737f8f0b3c768f3","tid":1701324,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:02:02.000Z","msg":"拉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:03:01.000Z","msg":"五毛好驚香港人知法庭唔係法治"},{"pid":"32d393c4c8e865058e192a96ef1cb6ccdb697fb1","tid":1701324,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:08:11.000Z","msg":"控方唔反對黃之峰出境、法官反對"},{"pid":"96fa2666d2aa75cc9586de6eb8d8bf0470ca5358","tid":1701324,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11